    <item>
      <title>About</title>
      <link>https://fernantastic.github.io/panoramical-website/about/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://fernantastic.github.io/panoramical-website/about/</guid>
      <description>&lt;img &#xA;  src=&#34;https://fernantastic.github.io/panoramical-website/images/panoramical_indiecadeast.jpg&#34; &#xA;  alt=&#34;My photo&#34; &#xA;  style=&#34;width:100%; height:auto; display:block; margin:auto;&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;about&#34;&gt;About&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Panoramical (2015) is a &lt;strong&gt;collection of playful interactive landscapes&lt;/strong&gt;: part art installation, part musical instrument.&lt;br&gt;&#xA;With a mixer board controller to manipulate visuals and sounds and no predefined goals, players find beautiful combinations of shapes and soundscapes, setting the pace of their own audiovisual journey.&lt;br&gt;&#xA;The result is an immersive experience for players and spectators.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Panoramical been featured in museums and exhibits worldwide, and released as a downloadable PC game.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
